OL,4,G1300FImpossible
OL,5,     GThe quiz show where players must
OL,6,     Gavoid the Impossible answer to
OL,7,     Gstay in the competition. 21
OL,8,     Gpeople begin the week, but how
OL,9,     Gmany of them will survive to face
OL,10,     Gthe #10,000 question?
OL,11,G1345FMastermind
OL,12,     GClive Myrie hosts the classic
OL,13,     Gquiz where contenders take to the
OL,14,     Gblack chair. Specialist subjects
OL,15,     Ginclude Stephen Hawking, the
OL,16,     Gmusic of Radiohead and Theda Bara.
OL,17,G1415FLightning
OL,18,     GZoe Lyons hosts a quiz where
OL,19,     Gcontestants avoid the light to
OL,20,     Gwin a #3,000 jackpot.
